<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">cfPPetr3,53,I</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><app type="editorial"><lem>Ἀλκαῖος</lem><rdg><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ιων</rdg></app> Σωσιφάνει χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>χάρις τοῖς θε<add place="supralinear">ο</add>ῖς πολλὴ εἰ ὑγιαί-

    <lb n="3"/>νεις· ὑγιαίνει δὲ καὶ Λώνικος. 

    <lb n="4"/>πεφύτευται δὲ καὶ ἡ ἄμπε-

    <lb n="5"/>λος πᾶσα <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del> πυθμένες 

    <lb n="6"/>τριακόσιοι <num value="300"/> καὶ τὰ περὶ τὴν 

    <lb n="7"/>ἀναδενδράδα. τὸ δὲ ἔλαιον 

    <lb n="8"/>δέδωκεν χοῦς <num value="6">ϛ</num>.  τούτων 

    <lb n="9"/>ἔχει Δύνις <num value="3">γ</num>. ἐχρησάμην 

    <lb n="10"/>δὲ καὶ παρὰ Δύνεως ἀρτά-

    <lb n="11"/>βας <num value="4">δ</num> κριθοπυρῶν αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>ἐπαγγελομένου καὶ φιλοτίμου 

    <lb n="13"/>ὄντος. γίνωσκε δὲ καὶ ὅτι 

    <lb n="14"/>ὕδωρ ἕκαστος τῶν <choice><corr cert="low">ὁρών<supplied cert="low" reason="omitted">των</supplied></corr><sic>ορων</sic></choice> τὴν 

    <lb n="15"/>ἄμπελον φυτευομένην πρότερον 

    <lb n="16"/>δεῖν φασιν <app type="editorial"><lem>ὑπάρχειν</lem><rdg><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ὐ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δὲ ὑ</supplied>πάρχειν</rdg></app> 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>ὀχετεύομεν δὲ καὶ ποτίζομεν 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="editorial"><lem>εὐθὺς</lem><rdg>ἔτους</rdg></app> τὰ πρῶτα ιιι 

    <lb n="3"/>ἔρρωσο. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-201" notBefore="-300" type="textDate">III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Petr.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">29</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">7475</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0187</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">29</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0187;1;29" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">XXIX</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">P.Petr. III 53 (i)</bibl><bibl default="NO" subtype="other" type="publication">Witkowski, Epistulae privatae 18</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl default="NO" type="translations">Kloppenborg, Tenants in the Vineyard (2006), S. 443</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.7475" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName c